message.content: cs.AR, cs.AR is the most likely category as the paper deals with computer architecture and memory systems. cs.DC is also likely as it deals with data centers and their performance. cs.SE is another possible category as the paper proposes software-managed cache mechanisms. cs.PF is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses energy efficiency. cs.SY is also a possibility as the paper proposes hardware modifications to DRAM.
